task duration: Time taken to execute the operator
op type: Operator type, for example: con2d, pooling
task type: Task type, for example: AI Core, AI CPU, Vector Core
block dim: Number of AI Cores that execute the operator
aicore time: Time taken to execute all instructions
total cycles: Number of cycles taken to execute all instructions
vec ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Vector instructions
vec time: Time taken to execute Vector instructions
mac ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Cube instructions
mac time: Time taken to execute Cube instructions
scalar ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Scalar instructions
scalar time: Time taken to execute Scalar instructions
mte1 ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute MTE1 instructions (L1-to-L0A/L0B movement)
mte1 time: Time taken to execute MTE1 instructions (L1-to-L0A/L0B movement)
mte2 ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute MTE2 instructions (DDR-to-AI Core movement)
mte2 time: Time taken to execute MTE2 instructions (DDR-to-AI Core movement)
mte3 ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute MTE3 instructions (AI Core-to-DDR movement)
mte3 time: Time taken to execute MTE3 instructions (AI Core-to-DDR movement)
mac fp16 ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Cube fp16 instructions
mac int8 ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Cube int8 instructions
vec fp32 ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Vector fp32 instructions
vec fp16 ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Vector fp16 instructions
vec int32 ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Vector int32 instructions
vec misc ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute Vector misc instructions
vec bankgroup conflict ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute vec_bankgroup_stall_cycles instructions
vec bank conflict ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute vec_bank_stall_cycles instructions
vec resc conflict ratio: Percentage of cycles taken to execute vec_resc_cflt_ratio instructions
memory bound: Data movement efficiency, calculated as: MTE2/Max(MAC, VEC)
vector bound: Vector utilization, calculated as: VEC/Max(MTE2, MTE3, MAC)
